data.text:
published on 2021-04-17T10:14:12Z

Active German artist and producer Droste is back in the studio and releases his new single on Locked-In, Mindscape. The track delivers a fusion of jackin' and micro house, featuring a groovy deep bass, a funky guitar line, and glitchy elements. Follow Locked-In on Facebook: www.facebook.com/locked.in.ams/ on Soundcloud: @locked-in-dam on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/locked.in.dam/
